text: Kiamwangi is a settlement in Kenya's Central Province.Kiamwangi is located about 25 kilometers from Nairobi. It has been described as a socio-economic village due to its attribution to numerous social and economic activities Kiamwamwangi neighbors Ishaweri village, the home of the first and the fourth presidents of Kenya. == References == Category:Populated places in Central Province (Kenya) It has one big primary school kiamwangi primary school.
title: Kiamwangi
